        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group quote-modified\" data-post=\"5\" data-topic=\"178183\">\n<blockquote>\n<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-post=\"3\" data-topic=\"178183\">\n<blockquote>\n<p>Have you tried the 2019 of this yet?  If so, I\u2019d be interested to hear your thoughts.  Thanks!</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>No, I haven\u00b4t. But I assume that 2019 is even better, as 2018 is a warm year and 2019 clearly a better vintage.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Thanks!  When I pop one I\u2019ll share a TN.  Looks like nobody has posted one on CT yet.</p>",
